@startuml
title StateSpec Runtime Binding OCC Model

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Generated service / workflow" as Service

interface "Backend / IBackend" as Backend
interface "Transaction / ITransaction" as Tx

component "Entity store" as Entity
component "FeatureFlagStore" as FeatureFlags
component "QueueStore" as Queue
component "LeaseStore" as Lease
component "WorkflowStore" as Workflow

database "Versioned persisted state" as Store

Service --> Backend : begin()
Backend --> Tx : open transaction

Service --> Entity : get / put via Tx
Service --> FeatureFlags : evaluateTx(...)
Service --> Queue : enqueueTx / claimTx(...)
Service --> Lease : acquireTx / renewTx(...)
Service --> Workflow : startTx / completeTx(...)

Entity --> Tx
FeatureFlags --> Tx
Queue --> Tx
Lease --> Tx
Workflow --> Tx

Tx --> Store : OCC reads and writes
Service --> Backend : commit(tx)

note bottom of Tx
All persisted reads that affect behavior
participate in the same optimistic
concurrency transaction as writes.
end note

note right of FeatureFlags
Feature flag evaluation is persisted-state
access, so generated code uses Tx-aware
binding APIs.
end note

@enduml
